{"tid":1046083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記最後的劇情","createTime":"2019-03-04T03:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T03:48:31.000Z","uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c28ec6c178f8a3c7421e92e159cc0d92b519889d","tid":1046083,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/112832_102a5356c759c2b88ac0d19eba0672df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F112832_102a5356c759c2b88ac0d19eba0672df.jpg&h=03faaa78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n響剩餘的賽事中全勝下尾二俾賓帥了結左希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賓帥既戰術係放棄左擅長既防反戰術,擺個全攻陣放水利記<br />\n但最終結果係疲倦之師利記俾力,俾紐記大炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賓帥會唔會由最愛的人成為背插一刀既兇手"},{"pid":"c11307170be8c8970097650c147fa887070ee68a","tid":1046083,"uid":162509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會係最尾比狼咬易啲"},{"pid":"62be53390ac2174021ff734e816b9fa4389da498","tid":1046083,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"8場波<br />\n場場都易食<br />\n如無意外應該嬴晒<br />\n相反曼城仲要對死曼狗<br />\n而家就望死曼狗幫一幫我地殺曼城<br />\n等我地可以重奪英超冠軍<br />\n死曼狗，幫幫手唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cc2ce33aa9fd7fa7f94776db834552cca39668","tid":1046083,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"啲對手舒服到"},{"pid":"edef19a050a253228e37def4c09eadde3b0a1a64","tid":1046083,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c11307170be8c8970097650c147fa887070ee68a","tid":1046083,"uid":162509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會係最尾比狼咬易啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"紐卡素上升緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對曼城都可以贏 <br />\n狼隊真係見得到實力終點"}]}